pageContext.claim: “So with Luther, so I have a list and one of the names is Luther Strange. And I know he's the senator from Alabama, but I don't know him, I met him once. I said that is the tallest human being I've ever seen. I'm tall. I'm tall. I never saw something -- he's, like, he should be on the New York Nicks, they could use him. So that's why I call him 'Big Luther,' everyone is now calling him 'Big Luther.'”
pageContext.analysis: Trump did not invent the nickname "Big Luther."
